---
title: Lobster BLTs with a Caesar Side Salad
description: There are three types of people: those who always choose a classic BLT, those who want to bite into a lobster roll, and those who can’t decide between the two. Our chefs found a way for you to have it all with tonight’s mashup meal: Presenting the Lobster BLT! You’ll heat up bacon, then cook lobster in the delicious pan drippings for a flavorful and crispy twist. To add another classic favorite on the side, you’ll prepare a Caesar salad studded with even more bacon. We’re pretty sure you’ll be wishing every sandwich menu listed the LBLT from now on…
